  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rising for Blind Children - Education4Blind</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">One of the hardest disabilities for children to overcome (or adjust to) is blindness. They explore &amp; see the world with their hands, they need to learn braille system &amp; access to braille books in young age in order to build core knowledge &amp; literacy. If they don&apos;t go to school, or lack the adequate resources for enrichment, they fall behind socially, and get isolated from the society.   This project is going to create a fund to support their education &amp; enrichment.</narrative>
  </description>
